    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">For orders made with the "cash on delivery" option, the user pays for the goods and delivery to the courier company upon receipt of the goods.</span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">For orders paid by debit or credit card, the price is pre-calculated and upon receipt of the goods, the user does not owe any other fees.</span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;"><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt;">It is possible to accept goods ordered from the ONLINE STORE in person at the physical stores of the SUPPLIER. In this case, the user does not pay a delivery fee.</span></em></span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;">&nbsp;</p>
