    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">The user can place order 24 hours a day, including weekends and holidays, and orders will be processed within the first 2 business days.</span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">If the user wishes to register, it is necessary to enter data such as delivery address, name, surname, phone number, email and password. After registration, the user has the opportunity to log into his account with the already entered email and password.</span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">When shopping as a "GUEST", the user enters only the necessary data for delivery, namely: delivery address, name, surname and telephone number.</span></span></p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">After placing an order, each user will be notified of the status of their order by email or phone contact.</span></span></p>
