    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">The store makes no commitment that all goods offered are available at the time of order and the product may be out of stock due to sales from the physical store or other place. If a product is not available, the user will be notified and will be given options to choose and resolve the case.</span></span></p>
