    <p style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">By using the website, filling in his data and marking consent, the user declares that he is familiar with this page as well as with the privacy policy, agrees with their content and undertakes to unconditionally comply with them.</span></span></p>
